The Truth about Rust/WebAssembly Performance

Greg Johnston
Greg Johnston
8810 Abonnenten
Herunterladen
208.073 Aufrufe vor 2 Jahren
208.073 Aufrufe 17.03.2023
Over the last six months, frontend frameworks written in Rust and WebAssembly have begun overturning the old narrative that WASM is too slow for DOM rendering. In this video we'll take a look at several Rust/WASM frameworks to try to understand the truth about Rust/WASM performance.  ...mehr
...mehr
Weniger anzeigen
This video explores the performance of several Rust/WebAssembly frontend frameworks. It debunks common myths about WASM speed and DOM rendering, using the js-framework-benchmark for comparison. The analysis delves into code examples to illustrate performance differences between frameworks.
